00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:39,440
Vôbec nič si nepamätáte?

227
00:20:40,870 --> 00:20:42,460
Prosím?

228
00:20:42,460 --> 00:20:43,970
Povedali ste, že vám zmizli spomienky.

229
00:20:43,970 --> 00:20:52,200
